Package: rTrafa
Title: Access Swedish Transport Statistics from the 'Trafa' API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Love", "Hansson", , email = "love.hansson@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Description: A pipe-friendly R client for the Trafa statistical API
    (api.trafa.se). Provides a search-then-fetch workflow for discovering
    and downloading Swedish transport and infrastructure data using a
    consistent tibble-based interface.
License: AGPL (>= 3)
URL: https://lchansson.github.io/rTrafa/, https://github.com/lchansson/rTrafa
BugReports: https://github.com/lchansson/rTrafa/issues
